OL,3,CAsda workers to strike for 48 hours
OL,4,Cover claims of 'toxic environment'
OL,6,FWorkers at the Asda store in Gosport
OL,7,Fin Hampshire are to stage a 48-hour
OL,8,Fstrike over claims of a "toxic"
OL,9,Fworking environment.
OL,11,FMembers of the GMB at the site at the
OL,12,FCranbourne Industrial Estate will walk
OL,13,Fout on Friday until midnight on
OL,14,FSaturday.
OL,16,FThe union said its members had
OL,17,Frejected a company offer aimed at
OL,18,Fresolving the row.
