OL,3,CAsda workers to strike for 48 hours
OL,4,Cover claims of 'toxic environment'
OL,6,FRegional officer Nicola Nixon said:
OL,7,F"Counter-proposals have ben made to
OL,8,Fthe company to settle the dispute but
OL,9,FAsda has failed to come back with any
OL,10,Fimprovements.
OL,12,F"Our members should be able to come to
OL,13,Fwork without the threat of bullying or
OL,14,Fputting their health, safety and
OL,15,Fwellbeing at risk."
OL,17,FAsda has reassured customers that the
OL,18,Fmajority of staff will be working as
OL,19,Fnormal and that they expect disruption
OL,20,Fto be minimal.
