OL,6,FAn Asda spokesperson said: "We have
OL,7,Fmet the GMB on several occasions
OL,8,Frecently, including mediation at Acas,
OL,9,Fto try and agree a fair solution for
OL,10,Fall colleagues in Gosport.
OL,12,F"The proposals we put forward include
OL,13,Fthe appointment of an independent
OL,14,Fthird-party organisation to establish
OL,15,Fthe facts regarding GMB's complaints
OL,16,Fand report back jointly to both
OL,17,Fparties.
OL,19,F"Unfortunately, this proposal was
OL,20,Frejected by the GMB membership.
